{"tid":1342730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗好多黑社會 唔好入去啦","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:38:07.000Z","uid":154176,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"318d420863051a36d8cf08e3a039a41fcd0b4d95","tid":1342730,"uid":154176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:54:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 ！<br />\n<br />\n我地呢幾個月抗爭 共產黨都未撚驚過啦 ！<br />\n<br />\n元朗嗰堆垃圾牛屎飛驚你有牙咩<br />\n<br />\n警察有槍有催淚彈都未撚驚<br />\n<br />\n驚你班中年肥撚呀叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次上面部署想用元朗引開注意 但行撚錯步<br />\n<br />\n諗住叫警察唔撚好理 比黑社會管治<br />\n<br />\n估唔到班垃圾冇腦到沖入車廂 見人就打<br />\n<br />\n依家藍絲數目下降 全港人憤怒值100<br />\n<br />\n我家兩佬都成功放棄支持藍絲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ad6337c9dd196f58f7cae318867acf77e95e75","tid":1342730,"uid":154176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc320b96c8f156a7f105e5b2ed281016035b5f7f","tid":1342730,"uid":154176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e946ee8cb93731fd9384f04af7b78b2b571bd91","tid":1342730,"uid":154176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\"